726561f-a.title: Queens: Farmers Boulevard - 133rd Road
726561f-a.text:
Farmers Boulevard, west side, between 133rd Road and
133rd Avenue, viewing north and showing the William Derermer
ouse. Wolverton's 1891 map shows it to be the property of
R. Doremus.
View 1: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  September, 1923
MAY BE REPRODUCED
View 2: P. L. Sperr  March 15, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
